{
  "chapter": 2,
  "chapter_summary": "本章讲述辛家村的辛鹏九夫妇携子辛捷隐居四年后，在五年之期最后一天被海天双煞找上门来。天残焦化、天废焦劳兄弟逼迫辛鹏九夫妇自尽，辛仪怒骂反抗却被焦化制服并当众凌辱。辛鹏九为保儿子性命忍辱负重，最终拼死一击杀死天废焦劳后殒命。海天双煞将十二岁的辛捷绑上狂牛抛出，牛狂奔闯入五华山深处。辛捷跌落雪地后醒来，遇到被点苍七绝手法重伤、功力尽失的七妙神君梅山民。梅山民被辛捷的遭遇所动，决定收留这个孤儿。二人相互扶持走出幽谷，辛捷的命运由此改变。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_peng_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "辛鹏九",
      "listener": "char_xin_yi",
      "text": "这几年来，真是苦了你，总算现在已经挨过五年了，只要挨过今夜，日后我们的心事也就了却了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_yi",
      "speaker_name": "辛仪",
      "listener": "char_xin_peng_jiu",
      "text": "就算日后没事，我也不愿再入江湖了，就好好在这里做个安分良民吧，那种拿刀动剑的日子，我真过得腻了。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_peng_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "辛鹏九",
      "listener": "char_xin_yi",
      "text": "说实话，这几年来，我倒真个有些静极思动了，要不是那个魔头太过厉害，我早已熬不住了，幸亏……",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_yi",
      "speaker_name": "辛仪",
      "listener": "char_xin_peng_jiu",
      "text": "要是过了今夜，他们仍不放松呢？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_peng_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "辛鹏九",
      "listener": "char_xin_yi",
      "text": "那倒不会，海天双煞虽是心毒手辣，但二十年来，却是言出必行，只要过了他立下五年之期，五年之后，就是我们和他们对面遇上，他们都不会伤我们一根毫毛的。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_can_jiao_hua",
      "speaker_name": "天残焦化",
      "listener": "char_xin_peng_jiu",
      "text": "辛老六倒真是我的知己，就冲你这句话，我焦老大让你死个痛快。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 61
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_peng_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "辛鹏九",
      "listener": "char_tian_can_jiao_hua",
      "text": "大哥，二哥既然来了，何不请下来？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_can_jiao_hua",
      "speaker_name": "天残焦化",
      "listener": "char_xin_peng_jiu",
      "text": "你真的还要我费事动手吗？盏茶之内，你夫妇父子三人，若不立刻自决，恐怕死得更惨了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 73
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_peng_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "辛鹏九",
      "listener": "char_tian_can_jiao_hua",
      "text": "我夫妇俩人自知对不起大哥、二哥，念在以前的情分，饶这小孩子一命。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_can_jiao_hua",
      "speaker_name": "天残焦化",
      "listener": "char_xin_peng_jiu",
      "text": "刚说你是我的知己，现在怎又说出这样的话来，难道你不知道我弟兄的脾气，还会让你们留后吗？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_yi",
      "speaker_name": "辛仪",
      "listener": "char_tian_can_jiao_hua",
      "text": "你们两个老残废，不要赶人入绝路，难道我们连不做强盗的自由都没有？要知道，我们滇桂双雕也不是好欺负的，我辛大娘倒要看看你们有什么通天彻地的本事",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_yi",
      "speaker_name": "辛仪",
      "listener": "char_tian_can_jiao_hua",
      "text": "鹏九还不跟他们拼了。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_can_jiao_hua",
      "speaker_name": "天残焦化",
      "listener": "char_xin_peng_jiu",
      "text": "辛老六，你若能不出这圈子一步，只是看着我弟兄二人处置你的老婆，我弟兄便破一次例，饶了这小孩的性命，否则你若要和我弟兄动手，也是悉听尊意，你看着办吧！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_can_jiao_hua",
      "speaker_name": "天残焦化",
      "listener": "char_xin_peng_jiu",
      "text": "好，辛老六，有你的，非但你这孩子的一条命，总算被你捡回来了，而且我焦老大一高兴，连你也饶了，你若仍然跟着我，我也仍然像以前一样的待你。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_peng_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "辛鹏九",
      "listener": "char_tian_can_jiao_hua",
      "text": "你答应在十年之内，决不伤这孩子。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_can_jiao_hua",
      "speaker_name": "天残焦化",
      "listener": "char_xin_peng_jiu",
      "text": "我焦老大言出必行，难道你还不知道？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_peng_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "辛鹏九",
      "listener": "char_tian_can_jiao_hua",
      "text": "好，那我就放心了。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_can_jiao_hua",
      "speaker_name": "天残焦化",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "真便宜了他，让他死得这么痛快。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_shan_min",
      "speaker_name": "梅山民",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "不要动，再躺一会。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 299
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_shan_min",
      "speaker_name": "梅山民",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "你这小孩，怎会骑着狂牛，跑到这里来，你是谁？你的家住在什么地方？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_shan_min",
      "speaker_name": "梅山民",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "你别哭，有什么难过的事，只管对我讲。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_shan_min",
      "speaker_name": "梅山民",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "你知道我是谁吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 367
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_shan_min",
      "speaker_name": "梅山民",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "现在你也是无亲可靠了，你可愿跟随着我？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 373
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_mei_shan_min",
      "text": "好，我一定跟随着你，照顾着你，你别看我现在浑身没有力气，只要我歇一会儿，我力气倒大得很，什么事都能做的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_shan_min",
      "speaker_name": "梅山民",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "好，好，我正需要你的照顾呢。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_shan_min",
      "speaker_name": "梅山民",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "你能不能站起来，扶着我走出这山谷去？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 384
    }
  ],
